Four Tanky Skimmers humming by!

 There are two Hulls included, main difference being the placment
of the turret, HummerHull 1 is off center, HummerHull 2 is perfectly centered.

All the four versions have an fully assembled model included, but you also get the turrets and gun mounts separately, as well as full gun turrets.

So printing turrets and guns separately, allows you to pose the gun at a wanted angle. A ready gun turret naturally has the guns angle fixed.

Also all files come with a pre-supported option.
Four printable bases included


Suitablr for 6-8mm

8 models packed with heavy firepower!

three different sets

Type A:
 Carry two guns on their arms and pack missiles topside.

Type B:
 Have their guns on a shoulder rig and carry MissilePodGloves

Type C:
 Missiles as type A, but carry one BIG Heavy Gun


I have included pre-supported as well as unsupported files for all models.

Also I've thrown in some bases made for these models that can be printed in FDM as well as resin.

All filenames end with a "+" followed by a small letter, this corresponds to the base that will fit them tiny little feet.

There are five bases in total, "a", "b" and "c" will go with two models each.
"x" and "z" are unique to their specific models


808 Thick Guns are
Suitable for 6mm gaming
